{
  "title": "打倒群里的柚子厨",
  "description": "欢乐吐槽群里的“柚子厨风波”，在笑闹中走向和解。",
  "segments": [
    {
      "text": "哎，这柚子厨又在群里发柚子图片了，每天都是柚子，我都看腻了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "1",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "是啊，我也觉得，感觉他生活中就只有柚子一样。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "2",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "我倒是好奇，他到底有多喜欢柚子啊？",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "3",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "你们看，他又发了一篇柚子的营养价值，真是没完没了了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "4",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "群里的气氛开始有些微妙，大家对这个“柚子厨”有些厌倦了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "next": "5",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "大家看看，这个柚子的果肉多饱满，真是太好吃了！",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "柚子厨",
      "next": "6",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_柚子厨_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "（私信李晓芳）这柚子厨真是的，每天都是柚子，我都想屏蔽他了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "7",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "（私信张大明）我也是，但是屏蔽他又觉得不太好，毕竟他是群里的活跃分子。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "8",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "（在群里发）柚子厨，你能不能换个话题啊？我们都被你刷屏了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "9",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "（附和）是啊，虽然柚子很好，但是我们也不能天天吃啊。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "10",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "我只是想分享我喜欢的柚子，没想到大家会这么反感。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "柚子厨",
      "next": "11",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_柚子厨_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "柚子厨有些失落，他没想到自己的热情会引来大家的反感。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "next": "12",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "（想了想）要不我们搞个“柚子主题日”吧？这样柚子厨也能满足，我们也觉得新鲜。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "13",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "这个主意不错，我们可以一起参与，让柚子厨看看柚子也可以玩出新花样。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "14",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "好啊，我赞成，这样群里的气氛也会活跃一些。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "15",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "那我们就这么办吧，到时候让柚子厨也参与进来。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "16",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "大家开始策划“柚子主题日”，气氛逐渐变得轻松起来。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "next": "17",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_tension.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "（看到群里的消息）“柚子主题日”？这是为我准备的吗？",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "柚子厨",
      "next": "18",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_柚子厨_excited_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "是啊，柚子厨，我们想让你知道，柚子也可以有很多玩法。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "19",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "对啊，你也可以分享一些柚子的其他用途，不只是吃的。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "20",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "我们可以一起做柚子料理，或者柚子手工艺品。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "21",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "还可以举办柚子知识问答，看谁对柚子了解最多。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "22",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "柚子厨听了大家的话，心里暖暖的，他决定好好准备一下。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "next": "23",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "谢谢大家，我会准备一些有趣的柚子小知识，到时候和大家分享。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "柚子厨",
      "next": "24",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_柚子厨_excited_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "太好了，那我们就期待你的表现了！",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "25",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "是啊，柚子厨，你一定会做得很好的。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "26",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "到时候我们可以一起玩得开心一些。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "27",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "对啊，让我们的群里充满欢声笑语。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "28",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "“柚子主题日”当天，群里的气氛非常热烈，大家都积极参与其中。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "next": "29",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": "大家看，这是我做的柚子手工艺品，是不是很有趣？",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "柚子厨",
      "next": "30",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_柚子厨_excited_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "哇，真的很好看！你手真巧！",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "张大明",
      "next": "31",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_张大明_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "这个柚子料理也很好吃，没想到柚子还能这么玩。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "李晓芳",
      "next": "32",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_李晓芳_calm_v2.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "是啊，今天的活动真的很成功，大家都玩得很开心。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "王强",
      "next": "33",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_王强_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "最重要的是，我们和柚子厨之间的误会也解开了。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "赵小美",
      "next": "34",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      },
      "character_image": "assets/char_赵小美_calm_v1.png"
    },
    {
      "text": "通过“柚子主题日”，大家不仅发现了柚子的多种玩法，还增进了彼此之间的友谊。",
      "effect": "typewriter",
      "speed": 55,
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "background": {
        "image": "assets/scene_group_chat_festival.png"
      }
    }
  ],
  "shared": {
    "planning": {
      "requirements_summary": "本项目旨在创作一部以网络群聊中的搞笑日常为题材的视觉小说，主要面向成年受众。故事围绕一群性格迥异的群友展开，通过一系列轻松幽默的事件，展现他们之间的友情与日常趣事，最终达成和解与理解。",
      "script_form": "visual_novel",
      "planning_source": "ai_auto",
      "worldview": "故事发生在一个名为“欢乐吐槽群”的网络群聊中，群成员来自不同的背景，但都热爱生活，喜欢在群里分享各种趣事和吐槽。群里有一个被称为“柚子厨”的成员，因其对柚子的极端热爱和频繁提及而闻名，但也因此引发了不少群友的不满。",
